ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Pesquisou na web</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Pesquisou na web</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Pesquisa feita. O diagnóstico é claro e a solução também. Vou aplicar agora.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>O problema atual:</strong> Syne no body text é bonito mas foi projetado para display — pesado demais em parágrafos. DM Sans nos títulos perde impacto. A hierarquia está invertida.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>A solução baseada na pesquisa:</strong> A abordagem mais eficaz para SaaS é parear uma fonte de heading distinta com uma fonte de body otimizada para leitura em tela. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://fullstop360.com/blog/insights/branding/saas-typography-playbook-what-leading-companies-use" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">FullStop</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span> Vou usar:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Plus Jakarta Sans</strong> nos títulos — features clean lines, geometric forms, e uma presença confiante na tela, perfeita para SaaS e startups modernas <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://stylokit.com/blog/top-20-fonts-for-modern-web-design-2025" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Stylokit</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Manrope</strong> no body — projetada especificamente para legibilidade em tela, com foco em UI, numerais alinhados e espaçamento generoso <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://shakuro.com/blog/best-fonts-for-web-design" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Shakuro</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tamanhos e pesos ajustados para hierarquia clara</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Editou 2 arquivos</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Editou 2 arquivos</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Agora atualizo todas as referências de fonte nos elementos — títulos, nav, badges, seções:</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Executou 3 comandos</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Executou 3 comandos</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Agora ajusto os tamanhos e pesos para hierarquia de leitura clara:</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Editou 13 arquivos, leu um arquivo</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Editou 13 arquivos, leu um arquivo</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>O que a pesquisa mostrou:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Inter aparece em 182 dos 500+ sites SaaS catalogados — o que cria um problema: a fonte segura virou invisível. As empresas que se destacam estão migrando para duplas distintas: fonte de display marcante nos títulos + fonte de body otimizada para leitura. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://fullstop360.com/blog/insights/branding/saas-typography-playbook-what-leading-companies-use" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">FullStop</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>O que foi aplicado:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Plus Jakarta Sans</strong> nos títulos — geométrica, confiante, leitora em qualquer tamanho, usada por SaaS modernos e startups. Substituiu o Syne que era bonito mas pesado demais para títulos longos em dark background.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Manrope</strong> no body — projetada especificamente para legibilidade em tela, com numerais alinhados e espaçamento generoso, mantendo clareza tanto em parágrafos quanto em elementos de UI. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://shakuro.com/blog/best-fonts-for-web-design" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Shakuro</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span> Substituiu o DM Sans que ficava leve demais em fundo escuro.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Além das fontes, ajustei toda a escala tipográfica:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Cor dos parágrafos de <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem] inline-flex items-center h-5"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 border-[0.5px] border-border-200 rounded flex-shrink-0 shadow-sm mr-1 align-middle" style="background-color: rgb(122, 138, 170);"></span>#7a8aaa</code> para <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem] inline-flex items-center h-5"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 border-[0.5px] border-border-200 rounded flex-shrink-0 shadow-sm mr-1 align-middle" style="background-color: rgb(168, 184, 208);"></span>#a8b8d0</code> — mais contraste sem ser branco cru</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">line-height</code> de 1.6 para 1.7–1.75 em todos os textos descritivos</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tamanho dos cards subiu de 0.875rem para 0.925rem</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">font-weight</code> dos subtítulos ajustado para 400 ao invés de 300 — 300 some em tela escura</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Títulos H1 maiores com <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">letter-spacing</code> mais apertado — impacto sem perder legibilidade</li>
</ul></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Index. Abrir artefato."><div class="artifact-block-cell group/artifact-block flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M67.84,92.61,25.37,128l42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,1-7.68,9.22l-48-40a6,6,0,0,1,0-9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,1,7.68,9.22Zm176,30.78-48-40a6,6,0,1,0-7.68,9.22L230.63,128l-42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,0,7.68,9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,0,0-9.22Zm-81.79-89A6,6,0,0,0,154.36,38l-64,176A6,6,0,0,0,94,221.64a6.15,6.15,0,0,0,2,.36,6,6,0,0,0,5.64-3.95l64-176A6,6,0,0,0,162.05,34.36Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">Index</div><div class="text-xs line-clamp-1 text-text-400 opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200">Código<span class="opacity-50"> · </span>HTML&nbsp;</div></div></div><div class="flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 shrink-0"><button class="inline-flex
