</span></span><span><span>        resultado</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">[</span><span>key</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">]</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240);">=</span><span> val_str
</span></span><span><span>    </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">return</span><span> resultado</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Chame antes de passar pro contexto:</p>
<div role="group" aria-label="Código python" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
