</span><span><span>    </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">return</span><span> render</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">(</span><span>request</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">,</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">"home.html"</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">,</span><span> context</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">)</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Duas correções além da <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sanitizar_exif</code>:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>1. Bug corrigido</strong> — no código original, o bloco de <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">original_b64</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">anon_b64</code> e <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">metadados</code> estava <strong>dentro</strong> do <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">if lat is not None</code> — ou seja, imagens <strong>sem GPS não geravam resultado nenhum</strong>. Movi esses blocos para fora do if, então agora funciona com qualquer imagem.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>2. <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sanitizar_exif</code> aplicada</strong> com <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">if exif else {}</code> para não quebrar se o <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">exif</code> vier <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">None</code>.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
