t-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Editou um arquivo, executou um comando, leu um arquivo</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Editou um arquivo, executou um comando, leu um arquivo</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Tudo aplicado. O que foi feito:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Mobile completo:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Hero, drop area, botão e hints adaptados para tela pequena</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Trust bar vira grid 2x2 em telas muito pequenas (&lt; 480px)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Todos os grids → 1 coluna abaixo de 768px</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Nav links some em mobile (já existia), padding ajustado</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Seções com padding reduzido para não desperdiçar espaço</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Terminal do choque com fonte menor e título escondido</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Botões 100% de largura em mobile para fácil toque</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Página de resultado melhorada:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Header de resultado</strong> com título "✅ Imagem limpa e pronta" + botões de ação no topo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Botão "Limpar nova imagem"</strong> que redireciona para <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/</code> — limpa tudo e volta ao início</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Botão de download</strong> agora aparece duas vezes — no header e dentro do card — em verde destacado com sombra</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Card "Anonimizada"</strong> com borda verde sutil para diferenciar visualmente</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Bloco do mapa</strong> com borda vermelha para reforçar o perigo que existia</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>CTA de compartilhamento</strong> no final do resultado — usa <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">navigator.share</code> nativo no mobile (abre share sheet do celular) e fallback para WhatsApp no desktop</li>
</ul></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Home. Abrir artefato."><div class="artifact-block-cell group/artifact-block flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M67.84,92.61,25.37,128l42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,1-7.68,9.22l-48-40a6,6,0,0,1,0-9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,1,7.68,9.22Zm176,30.78-48-40a6,6,0,1,0-7.68,9.22L230.63,128l-42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,0,7.68,9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,0,0-9.22Zm-81.79-89A6,6,0,0,0,154.36,38l-64,176A6,6,0,0,0,94,221.64a6.15,6.15,0,0,0,2,.36,6,6,0,0,0,5.64-3.95l64-176A6,6,0,0,0,162.05,34.36Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">Home</div><div class="text-xs line-clamp-1 text-text-400 opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200">Código<span class="opacity-50"> · </span>HTML&nbsp;</div></div></div><div class="flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 shrink-0"><button class="inline-flex
