ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Vou fazer uma leitura completa do HTML atual antes de recomendar qualquer coisa:</p></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Visualizou 3 arquivos</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Visualizou 3 arquivos</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Li tudo. Aqui está meu diagnóstico honesto:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Problemas reais encontrados</h2>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">🔴 Críticos — quebram UX</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>1. Ordem das seções está errada</strong>
O fluxo atual é: Hero → Trust Bar → Choque → Resultado → <strong>Problema → Para quem → Como funciona → Tecnologia → Benefícios → Credibilidade</strong>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">O problema é que <strong>"O problema" aparece DEPOIS do resultado</strong>. Quando o usuário faz upload, rola para o resultado e nunca mais vê as seções de educação. E para quem chega sem fazer upload, o "Choque" (terminal) está bem, mas aí cai direto no resultado vazio e depois nas seções. O fluxo correto seria:</p>
<div role="group" aria-label="Código" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
  items-center
  justify-center
  relative
  isolate
  shrink-0
  can-focus
  select-none
  disabled:pointer-events-none
  disabled:opacity-50
  disabled:shadow-none
  disabled:drop-shadow-none border-transparent
          transition
          font-base
          duration-300
          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_1abo4_9 _ghost_1abo4_96" type="button" aria-label="Copiar para a área de transferência" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span><span>Hero (upload) → Trust Bar → Choque → Problema → Para quem 
</span></span><span>→ Como funciona → Tecnologia → Benefícios → Credibilidade</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">O resultado aparece logo após o upload, acima de tudo isso, via scroll automático — não precisa estar intercalado na estrutura.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>2. <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;span id="tecnologia"&gt;</code> solta antes da section</strong>
A ancora de tecnologia está num <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;span&gt;</code> separado em vez de no próprio <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;section id="tecnologia"&gt;</code>. Isso faz o scroll do nav pular para o lugar errado.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>3. <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">problem-visual</code> menciona "anonimg" em vez de "Anonymizer"</strong>
Linha 1151: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">→ Removido com anonimg</code> — nome antigo exposto ao usuário.</p>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">🟡 Melhorias de estrutura</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>4. Benefícios e Tecnologia estão repetindo informação</strong>
A seção de Tecnologia explica "reconstrução RGB" e a seção de Benefícios tem "Proteção forense" dizendo a mesma coisa. Dá para fundir as duas ou pelo menos diferenciar melhor o foco.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>5. CSS morto</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.cta-section</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.cta-box</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.cta-btn</code> ainda existem no CSS mas a seção foi removida. São ~30 linhas de CSS inúteis.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>6. Duas linhas em branco antes do footer</strong> (linhas 1386–1387) — cosmético mas bagunçado.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Quer que eu aplique tudo isso? Posso fazer em uma rodada só — reordenar as seções, corrigir o id da tecnologia, atualizar o nome, limpar o CSS morto e corrigir o problem-visual.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
