lative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">O bloco GPS agora tem três partes conectadas visualmente:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>1. Cabeçalho de alerta</strong> — fundo vermelho suave com ícone 📍, título em vermelho "Localização exposta — qualquer pessoa poderia saber onde você estava" e subtítulo explicando que foi removida.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>2. Tabela de endereço</strong> — Rua, Bairro, Cidade/Estado, País, CEP em linhas separadas com labels em maiúsculo. Conectado ao cabeçalho sem borda entre eles.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>3. Rodapé com mapa</strong> — coordenadas formatadas com <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">floatformat:6</code> (só 6 casas decimais, sem aquele <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">-30.062758333333335</code> feio), botão "Ver no Google Maps" ao lado, e o iframe do mapa embaixo. Tudo no mesmo card com borda vermelha unificada.</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Home. Abrir artefato."><div class="artifact-block-cell group/artifact-block flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M67.84,92.61,25.37,128l42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,1-7.68,9.22l-48-40a6,6,0,0,1,0-9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,1,7.68,9.22Zm176,30.78-48-40a6,6,0,1,0-7.68,9.22L230.63,128l-42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,0,7.68,9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,0,0-9.22Zm-81.79-89A6,6