<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">E no <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">urls.py</code> principal (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">core/urls.py</code>) servir na raiz:</p>
