<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Para usar: clica com botão direito na imagem → "Salvar como" → salva como <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">og-image.png</code> → coloca em <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">anonymizer/static/anonymizer/img/og-image.png</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ela vai aparecer como preview quando alguém compartilhar o link do Anonymizer no WhatsApp, LinkedIn, Twitter e Facebook.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
